Uppers made with 100% premium waterproof leather from an LWG Silver-rated tannery. Seam-sealed construction. Rustproof, speed lace hardware with lace hooks at top. Fully gusseted tongue. EVA footbed. EVA midsole. Solid rubber outsole with multi-directional lugs.                     You're sure to have an outdoor positive experience when you have these waterproof boots on your feet. They're comfortable, durable and great looking.             
